node.text: The stunning makeup guru, @nikita_dragun achieves a beautiful nose enhancement with a non surgical nose job using dermal filler injections to improve the appearance of the nose. We further lift the tip of the nose by injecting a drop of Botox into the depressor nasalis, the muscle that pulls down the nose. My goal is always to bringing out the desired natural beauty focusing on subtle changes 💞

node.title: The beautiful Nikita Dragun achieves a beautiful nose enhancement

node.text: Many of you have responded to my previous video about Under Eye Fillers asking what you could do instead. Fillers last for years and years and so do their complications which can include moving around and causing your under eye to look like a balloon. The best way to improve the under eye is with a good retinol cream or by coming to visit us for a radio frequency treatment combined with microneedling treatment that will help tighten the skin #KanodiaKnows

node.title: Know what you can do instead of Under Eye Fillers in today’s #KanodiaKnows

node.text:
@azramian had three septal bends completely obstructing her nasal airway, forcing her to be a mouth breather. 

Azra’s nasal septum was straightened and repositioned in its midline anatomical position, opening the nasal passage for the air to travel back to the throat and lungs without any obstruction. It’s crucial to straighten the septum all the way from the front to back and recognize the posterior (bony) part of the septum has to be straightened also. Posterior (back) part of the septum, which is normally bony, needs a special long instrument, which has to be navigated through the nostril, in order to accomplish a fully straight septum.

Patient Update 🤩 SCARLESS FINESSE Septo-rhinoplasty. Results 7 days post surgery and 2 years after.

This patient has 100% open nasal airway that has tremendously improved her quality of life. Preservation of the original character is crucial for a natural result. This patient has a stunning tip nostril complex, leading to the conclusion that it should not be touched.

node.text: Cast reveal for @keliannestankus 🤩 7 days post surgery - scarless closed rhinoplasty. The wisdom is not to change the nose, but to refine and finesse. Kelianne is able to continue her normal actives with no telltale sign of any surgical alteration. Icing is still very important over the next 4-6 weeks to minimize swelling.

node.text: The Non-Surgical Facelift - Morpheus8 is an advanced microneedling treatment with radio frequency developed to stimulate remodeling in the adipose tissue of the dermis. By targeting the deeper layers of the skin, the building blocks will reorganize themselves in a natural anti-aging process. Tiny needles penetrate the skin and heat the tissue to stimulate the production of collagen. @karlahops
